    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK450">
<l>pallār pakaikoḷaliṟ pattaṭutta tīmaittē </l>
<l>nallār toṭarkai viṭiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is tenfold more injurious to abandon the friendship of the good, than to incur the hatred of the many.</l>
            </lg>
